      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AL'S MEMORY (7) stuck on well last time to finish half a length back in second (24.80) at this track in a Grade 5 over 440m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Key chance in this line up. MISS GLAMOURPUSS (6) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 0.8 lengths second over 400m Bulli in 22.39. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Ready to find winning form. ZIPPING RUPERT (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (30.74) in a Grade 5 at Nowra. Has a good record at this journey. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. In the mix. NEBULAR STRATUS (1) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.",
